\pard\b\fs30 7. System Design\b0\fs24\par
\par
\pard\b\fs26 7.1 Package Structure\b0\fs24\par
\par
\pard The system is organized into packages to support modular programming.\par
\par
\f1\fs20 src/com/lawrence/transcript/\par
\f1\fs20   Main.java\par
\f1\fs20   TestHarness.java\par
\f1\fs20   exception/\par
\f1\fs20   formatter/\par
\f1\fs20   gui/\par
\f1\fs20   model/\par
