\pard\b\fs30 12. Challenges and Solutions\b0\fs24\par
\par
\pard | Challenge | Solution |\par
\pard |---|---|\par
\pard | Keeping the project modular | The code was separated into model, service, formatter, exception, and GUI packages. |\par
\pard | Preventing invalid records | A custom exception was used for validation. |\par
\pard | Showing OOP concepts clearly | The Course hierarchy and formatter interface were used to demonstrate inheritance, polymorphism, and abstraction. |\par
\pard | Avoiding wrong GPA calculations | GPA and CGPA were calculated from quality points and total credits. |\par
\pard | Running easily on Windows | run.bat and test.bat scripts were added. |\par
\par
